- Azure board is similar to Jira software - This is a project planning and management tool
    - Tracking user stories
    - Backlog items
    - Task
    - Features
    - Bugs / Defects

In the organisation setttings - Board - Process
1. Basic        -   Epics, Issues, Tasks to track the work
2. Agile        -   User stories, Epics, Tasks, Bugs, Featues    
3. Scrum        -   Product backlog items, bugs
4. CMMI         -   Capability Maturity Model Integration Process - requirements, change requests, risks and reviews

For every Process - we will have built in fields - we can explore this option in Boards - Process - Fields

